for taking care of my girls.

30:59.339 --> 31:01.005
My pleasure. It's nice
to finally meet you.

31:01.007 --> 31:03.642
Yeah. You can
call me Marmee.

31:03.644 --> 31:05.944
- And this here is Amy.
- Hello, Amy.

31:05.946 --> 31:07.811
Amy, Laurie.

31:07.813 --> 31:11.282
Uh, um.
[chuckles]

31:11.284 --> 31:13.385
I'm sorry. My hair's
a mess right now.

31:13.387 --> 31:17.321
- I was braiding it.
- I'm actually kind of digging the one-sided thing.

31:17.323 --> 31:19.390
You could start a trend
with that.

