<i>♪ For auld lang syne, my dear ♪</i>

33:06.132 --> 33:10.868
<i>♪ For auld lang syne ♪</i>

33:10.870 --> 33:13.538
<i>♪ We'll take
A cup of kindness yet ♪</i>

33:13.540 --> 33:15.540
- Oh, guys! It's almost time!
- [Marmee] Oh, no, no, no!

33:15.542 --> 33:16.774
Come on, come on!

33:16.776 --> 33:18.742
- Wait, wait, wait. Hurry up. Hurry up.
- [meows]

33:18.744 --> 33:21.846
[Laurie]
Okay, ten, nine, eight...

33:21.848 --> 33:29.020
- [all] Seven, six, five, four, three, two, one.
- Amy!

33:29.022 --> 33:35.092
- Happy New Year! Whoo!
- <i>♪ For auld lang syne, my dear ♪</i>

33:35.094 --> 33:39.030
- Happy New Year, honey.
- <i>♪ For auld lang syne ♪</i>

33:39.032 --> 33:40.098
- Kiss.
- I love you.

33:40.100 --> 33:42.000
- I love you.
- Happy new year!

33:42.002 --> 33:44.769
The March sister who's going to get
the New Year's Eve kiss from me...

33:44.771 --> 33:46.507
is...

33:48.975 --> 33:50.074
Goob!

33:50.076 --> 33:51.776
[girls laughing]

33:51.778 --> 33:56.580
At this time, I wish to propose
a new member to the club.

33:56.582 --> 33:59.184
- What?
- This nominee...

33:59.186 --> 34:03.887
deserves a chance and would be
deeply grateful to join our ranks.

34:03.889 --> 34:06.057
- Goob.
- No. No.

34:06.059 --> 34:11.195
Further, I believe this soldier will
add a unique voice to the platoon.

34:11.197 --> 34:12.663
[all]
Who?

34:12.665 --> 34:16.867
I nominate
Mr. Laurie Laurence.

34:16.869 --> 34:20.871
- Mm-hmm.
- No! No, no, no. That would be so embarrassing!

34:20.873 --> 34:23.208
I agree with Amy.
I mean, Private Winkle.

34:23.210 --> 34:24.275
He would just make fun of us.

34:24.277 --> 34:28.813
I give my word, as a soldier,
and as Staff Sergeant

34:28.815 --> 34:32.916
that he will not make fun of
our grievances or our oaths.

34:32.918 --> 34:35.954
He wants nothing more than
to be a full part of the PC!

34:35.956 --> 34:38.857
He's like our brother!
Guys, we have to do it!

34:38.859 --> 34:41.960
- What if he tells Brooke?
- I promise I won't tell a soul!

34:41.962 --> 34:43.895
- Traitor!
- [Meg] You've been in there the whole time?

34:43.897 --> 34:46.063
- I hardly heard anything.
- You heard everything!

34:46.065 --> 34:50.567
My fellow comrades. I come to you
as a lowly Private First Class!

34:50.569 --> 34:53.570
A faithful friend
and a keeper of secrets.

34:53.572 --> 34:57.478
As a token of my appreciation for your
consideration, I have brought you this.

35:03.049 --> 35:04.616
Whoa.

35:04.618 --> 35:07.619
[Meg] What is it? A birdhouse?

35:07.621 --> 35:11.088
- What's it for?
- Every club needs a secret mailbox.

35:11.090 --> 35:15.659
To keep our correspondence safely in
the hedge between our two nations.

35:15.661 --> 35:20.067
This one is for secrets,
never to be told.

35:24.904 --> 35:26.040
An alliance then?

35:27.907 --> 35:29.873
Well, then, Private.

35:29.875 --> 35:31.078
As General, I say...

35:32.244 --> 35:34.514
welcome
to the Pickwick Club.

35:35.147 --> 35:37.648
- [exhales]
- Yes!

35:37.650 --> 35:40.217
[girl]
Your sister's really not coming?

35:40.219 --> 35:43.755
She said she's not interested
in "primitive rituals."

35:43.757 --> 35:46.891
Tonight is going to be
anything but primitive.

35:46.893 --> 35:49.594
Oh!
Your step-mom is the best!

35:49.596 --> 35:51.098
I know, right?

35:53.299 --> 35:55.632
That's a cute little dress.

35:55.634 --> 35:58.538
- It was my grandma's.
- How couture.

35:59.239 --> 36:01.940
Just throwing this
out there.

36:01.942 --> 36:06.679
I think I might have something
a little bit more flattering.

36:07.913 --> 36:09.646
Totally goes with our color
scheme, don't you think?

36:09.648 --> 36:10.815
- Um...
- Here.

36:10.817 --> 36:12.250
You definitely have
the body for it.

36:12.252 --> 36:14.918
Yes, I would kill
for that stomach.

36:14.920 --> 36:16.788
- Really?
- Face it, Meg. You're hot.

36:16.790 --> 36:19.257
- Everyone knows you're hot.
- Especially Brian.

36:19.259 --> 36:20.991
I heard he was dating
Miss Cape Cod.

36:20.993 --> 36:23.563
Well, here's to
the best prom ever!

